Package: StatGeo
Title: Interactive Spatial Analysis and GIS Platform
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for spatial analysis and GIS,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for loading vector and
    raster data, spatial integration, and spatial statistics. Designed for
    teaching and research in ecology and biodiversity sciences.
